Description:
[b][color=#9a7dce]The Conspiracy Theorist[/color][/b] is a [color=#c28c8c]desperate soul[/color], searching for hidden magic in a world that has stripped individuals of of exactly that.  

They crave [color=#b37f7f]significance[/color] by uncovering [u][color=#a1a1a1]“truths”[/color][/u] that exist only in their imagination.  

Driven by [color=#b37f7f]fear[/color], [color=#b37f7f]frustration[/color], and a relentless need to feel [b]special[/b],  
they connect dots that were never meant to be connected.  

This perfect mix of [color=#b37f7f]paranoia[/color] and [color=#c28c8c]hopelessness[/color] makes them ideal pawns for a [color=#c28c8c][b]carefully laid plan[/b][/color].  

[b]Feed them stories![/b] [b]Whisper promises of secret knowledge![/b]  
Give them the [color=#7fa3a3]attention and magic[/color]they so desperately seek, and suddenly they’ll work tirelessly for your cause —  
convinced they are [u][b]heroes[/b][/u], never realizing they’re not even facing their demise.

They are especially [b]effective[/b] in [color=#a1a1a1]less densely populated countries[/color],  
where isolation from the real world and other people comes easily.
"

